products.Title: NIKE DUNK HIGH 1985 GREEN DENIM
products.Body (HTML): Worn well and well-worn, the Dunk returns once again to match the original shape, look and feel of the '85 high top. Sun-washed Enamel Green denim brings the Americana flair. Raw-edge detailing and contrast stitching add a free-spirited look to any 'fit. And the aged midsole delivers a little hook-shot spirit back to the streets. Lace up and take your game anywhere—in cushioned high-top comfort.
